thread.title: Cricket J.
thread.title_full: My Passport Photos reviewed by Cricket J.

author: Cricket J.
title: Cricket J.
text: I chose to use My passport photos after a bad experience at a local store. The picture looked like a mugshot and was printed poorly as well. I paid $19.95 for those pictures and they ended up in the garbage. My passport photos website was just what I needed. I took about 10 pictures at home and selected the one I liked best. I chose to pick them up at Walgreens so that they could be cut precisely with the photo trimmer. I recommend this company highly.
